title: When I try to view online match history, it comes up blank
body:
Title, I used to have this problem before Riot fixed it before back on 07/08/14. I tried the CHrome extension I was using before the fix, didn't work. I confirmed that it doesn't show up in Chrome, Firefox, and Edge. Am sad.
Help pls?

replies.body: I was able to look up your [match history ](http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-history/NA1/50968563)without any issues.  If you are still having an issue with this, try resetting your cache and cookies in case your browser got bogged up.  You can also try Incognito mode or another browser in case of an extension getting in the way.  Hope that helps!
Same for me, does not work in any browser.
